{"error": null, "result": {"nr": 19, "upvote_ids": [], "change_log": [{"type": "create", "when": "2015-03-03T23:36:38Z", "uid": "i6tx0nskPKr", "data": "i6txptmz8zn3m4", "anon": "no"}, {"uid": "hsfa0sawctb6v4", "to": "i6txptm6ld43m3", "when": "2015-03-04T05:27:41Z", "anon": "no", "data": "i6ua99bhl747bp", "type": "i_answer"}, {"type": "followup", "to": "i6txptm6ld43m3", "when": "2015-03-07T04:06:14Z", "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "anon": "no"}], "q_edits": [], "i_edits": [], "unique_views": 168, "bookmarked": 3, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "有关于多核处理器下&#xff0c;进程与线程的概念。", "content": "<p>我最开始对于多核处理的进程和线程的理解是&#xff1a; 系统<strong>只可以</strong>执行一个进程&#xff0c;通过快速的上下文切换实现多进程。但是线程可以同时在多核处理上并发执行&#xff0c;也就是说不需要进行上下文切换即可实现多线程同步的进行。</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>后来又翻书查看了一下&#xff0c;一下是查看的段落&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i6tx0nskPKr/i6txgwwptftf/1.png\" /></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>以下是1.9.1的段落&#xff1a;</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://d1b10bmlvqabco.cloudfront.net/attach/i5j09fnsl7k5x0/i6tx0nskPKr/i6txm3e6wl9q/2.png\" /></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>看完以后对于多核处理器的进程执行产生了迷惑。在多核处理下&#xff0c;是否还是只执行一个进程&#xff1f;超线程处理器是否是用并行的技术实现单核超线程&#xff1f;</p>", "created": "2015-03-03T23:36:38Z", "uid": "i6tx0nskPKr", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "request_instructor_me": false, "folders": ["quiz1"], "type": "question", "tag_good": [], "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-03T23:36:38Z", "t": 1433499928603, "id": "i6txptm6ld43m3", "status": "active", "tag_good_arr": [], "default_anonymity": "no", "my_favorite": false, "bucket_order": 2, "is_bookmarked": false, "is_tag_good": false, "bucket_name": "Today", "no_answer_followup": 0, "children": [{"folders": [], "bucket_order": 2, "config": {}, "history": [{"subject": "", "content": "<p>可以分为 <strong>操作系统</strong> 和 <strong>硬件</strong> 两个层面来考虑这个问题。</p>\n<p>从 <strong>操作系统</strong> 层面&#xff0c;大部分操作系统工作时都有多个进程&#xff0c;进程的执行需要靠处理器</p>\n<p>一般情况&#xff0c;单核处理器&#xff0c;一个瞬间执行着一个进程&#xff0c;而在更长的时间内可能交替执行了多个进程</p>\n<p>考虑多核处理&#xff0c;每个核的情况同单核处理器&#xff0c;但是由于有多个核&#xff0c;所以整机实际上一个瞬间执行着多个进程</p>\n<p>简单来说&#xff0c;一个处理器在执行一个进程的时候&#xff0c;硬件资源是未能很充分地利用起来的&#xff0c;所以超线程从 <strong>硬件</strong> 层面来理解是让处理器具备了同时执行多个线程的能力</p>", "created": "2015-03-04T05:27:41Z", "uid": "hsfa0sawctb6v4", "anon": "no"}], "data": {"embed_links": []}, "bucket_name": "Today", "is_tag_endorse": false, "children": [], "tag_endorse": [{"admin": false, "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "钟声华", "id": "i6tx0nskPKr", "photo": null}, {"admin": false, "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "crazyx", "id": "i6vm0bo5WgQ", "photo": null}, {"class_sections": ["课程设计_i5j09fnsl7k5x0"], "admin": true, "role": "instructor", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "Yu Chen", "id": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "photo": "1378950179_35.png"}, {"admin": false, "role": "student", "facebook_id": null, "us": false, "name": "hbisheng", "id": "i70lz5f0QKm", "photo": null}], "tag_endorse_arr": ["i6tx0nskPKr", "i6vm0bo5WgQ", "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "i70lz5f0QKm"], "created": "2015-03-04T05:27:41Z", "id": "i6ua99beksj7bo", "type": "i_answer"}, {"no_upvotes": 0, "uid": "hcrrjuyequh4bt", "bucket_name": "Week 3/1 - 3/7", "bucket_order": 8, "updated": "2015-03-07T04:06:14Z", "config": {}, "anon": "no", "data": {"embed_links": null}, "folders": [], "subject": "这里需要对“并行 parallel”和“并发 concurrent”两个概念很清楚。", "children": [], "type": "followup", "no_answer": 0, "created": "2015-03-07T04:06:14Z", "id": "i6yho2eh2a72lv"}], "request_instructor": 0, "tags": ["quiz1", "student"], "s_edits": [], "num_favorites": 1}, "aid": "iajgufx7qi128b"}